title: Wednesday’s prep tennis results
text:
Kennedy Catholic 4, Hazen 3 Singles —Francis Viloria, K, beat David Vaisar, H, 6-1, 6-0; Brendan Stoll, K, beat Avelyino Vargas, H, 6-1, 6-2; David Ritscher, K, beat Dylan Kittay, H, 6-3, 6-4; Hayden Wood, K, beat Sohil Shah, H, 1-6, 6-4, 10-7.
Doubles —SonLam Nguyen-Justin Nguyen, H, beat Haydon Clifton-Ben Xu, K, 6-4, 4-6, 10-7; Alan Li-Nathan Nagel, H, beat Connor Loats-Luke Tolton, K, 7-6 (9-7), 6-7 (2-7), 10-7; Logan Ricord-Tyler Holm, H, beat RJ Buenafe-Reed Ellis, K, 6-1, 6-4.
Shorewood 4, Mountlake Terrace 3 Singles —Jeremy Asndell, M, beat Gunnar Thorstenson, S, 6-1, 6-0; Kyle Bergquist, S, beat Minchoel Jung, M, 6-3, 6-7, 6-2; Hugh Graevert, S, beat Trevor Swanson, M, 6-0, 6-0; Peter Smith, S, beat Max Knibble, M, 6-3, 6-1.
Doubles —Adam Lorraine-Jake Peters, M, beat Jack Bong-Andrew Counter, S, 6-7, 7-5, 6-2; Drake Day-Max Leidig, M, beat Joseph Jong-Simon Forinash, S, 6-4, 6-1; Camron Hardford-Jack Stensrud, S, beat Alec Ung-Owen Jones, M, 6-1, 6-0.

Singles —Wesley Chan, O, beat Priever Pretorious, A, 6-4, 6-3; Reyhan Virani, O, beat Travis Coop, A, 6-1, 6-1.
Doubles —Alex Horvat-Declan Daly, O, beat Ryan Castillo-Daniel Damitio, A, 6-2, 6-2; Kevin Gartland-Quinn Clelland, O, beat Parker Sand-Trent Mosier, A, 6-2, 7-5; Charlie Hill-Guarav Nene, O, beat Andrew Sudol-Anthony Damitio, A, 6-2, 6-2.
Seattle Academy 4, University Prep 1 Singles —Anders Gibbons, S, beat Joshua Wah-Blumberg, U, 6-1, 6-0; Ezra Magarm, S, beat Michael Yang, U, 6-2, 6-1.
Doubles —Zamir Birnbach-Will Owen, S, beat Jason Mansfield-Wilson Mosier, U, 6-1, 6-0; Hyunrae Kim-Isaac Selby, U, beat Augie Bartlett-Robert Winton, S, 7-6(4), 3-6, 10-7; Richard Khang-George Eitel, S, beat Cooper Hollie-Mike Baldwin, U, 6-1, 5-7, 10-8.
